name: Johanna Tan
text: I think ang kailangan ma gets ng masses is that what little freebies or benefits they get is nothing compared to what the binays are getting from everyone's taxes.. Mas d nga lang maramdaman ng mga d nagbabayad ng taxes kaya suporta parin sila
